nsparent bg-secondary text-secondary-foreground hover:bg-secondary/80",destructive:"border-transparent bg-destructive text-destructive-foreground hover:bg-destructive/80",outline:"text-foreground"}},defaultVariants:{variant:"default"}});function Jt({className:e,variant:t,...n}){return a.jsx("div",{className:F(Fz({variant:t}),e),...n})}const zz={hiring:{category:"Hiring Process",items:[{id:"hiring-cost",question:"Are any costs involved to provide job-ready talent for hire?",answer:"No, hiring from TAP Academy is completely free. Moreover, we offer you a hassle-free experience throughout the process with a dedicated Interview Success Expert from our end."},{id:"available-roles",question:"What are the roles TAP Academy can help your company fill?",answer:`Our candidates are trained and ready for various roles including:
• Frontend Development (JavaScript, ReactJS)
• Full Stack Development (MERN Stack)
• Java Full Stack Development
• Software Development
• Web UI Development (HTML, CSS Flexbox)
and many more specialized roles based on your requirements.`},{id:"hiring-timeline",question:"How long will it take to hire a developer from TAP Academy?",answer:"You can onboard a candidate in less than a week. A clear job description and quick interview turnarounds can further reduce this duration."},{id:"profile-sharing",question:"What is your turnaround time? How soon can I get profiles?",answer:"You would receive profiles in 24-48 hours (working days) once our hiring expert receives the clear requirements."},{id:"hiring-steps",question:"What is the hiring process?",answer:`Our streamlined process includes:
1. Get in touch with our Hiring Expert and define your requirements
2. Receive profiles in 24-48 hours
3. Start your interview process with the candidates
4. Onboard the candidates in less than a week`},{id:"interview-mode",question:"Is the hiring process online or offline?",answer:"We suggest that the entire hiring process be online to ensure maximum candidate participation. However, we can accommodate offline processes if required."}]},candidates:{category:"Candidate Details",items:[{id:"tech-stack",question:"In what technologies are candidates trained in?",answer:`Our candidates are extensively trained in:
• HTML, CSS, Bootstrap
• JavaScript & React JS
• Python
• SQL
• Node JS
• Express JS
• Java & Spring Boot
• Test Automation (Unit & Integration Testing)
and much more...`},{id:"candidate-background",question:"Who are your candidates? How long are your candidates trained?",answer:"The majority of our candidates are fresher graduates who have been trained for 6-8 months on technologies like Frontend Essentials (HTML, CSS, JavaScript), React.js, Java, Spring, Hibernate, SQL etc."},{id:"skill-verification",question:"Do you assess or verify the candidates' skills?",answer:"Yes, we verify and vet candidates through rigorous assessments, mock tests, mock interviews, and more. The process ensures that companies receive apt profiles to conduct the interview process."},{id:"joining-timeline",question:"Are these candidates ready to join immediately?",answer:"Yes, our candidates are willing to join immediately after selection."},{id:"work-location",question:"Which locations are your candidates willing to work?",answer:"Our candidates hail from across the country. They're open to working from the majority of the locations in India. Currently, our candidates are working in 25+ cities."},{id:"joining-rate",question:"What is the probability of a candidate joining us if given an offer?",answer:"More than 97% of our candidates have joined the companies from which they received their first offer."}]}},Zw={general:{category:"General",items:[{id:"what-is-tap",question:"What is TAP Academy?",answer:"TAP Academy is a next-generation ed-tech platform dedicated to transforming the way students learn and launch their tech careers. We provide practical, industry-relevant skills training with expert mentorship and guaranteed placement support."},{id:"why-choose-tap",question:"Why choose TAP Academy over other coding bootcamps?",answer:"TAP Academy offers personalized mentorship, real-world project experience, guaranteed job placement, and a proven track record of 75,000+ successful upskilled  in top tech companies."},{id:"prerequisites",question:"Do I need prior coding experience to join?",answer:"No prior coding experience is required. Our courses are designed to take you from beginner to job-ready professional, starting with the fundamentals and building up to advanced concepts."},{id:"time-commitment",question:"How much time should I dedicate daily?",answer:"We recommend 2-3 hours daily for optimal learning. Our flexible schedule includes 90-minute live classes plus additional practice time to reinforce concepts."},{id:"learning-format",question:"What is the learning format?",answer:"We offer a hybrid learning approach with live interactive classes, recorded sessions for review, hands-on projects, and one-on-one mentorship sessions."},{id:"support-system",question:"What kind of support do you provide?",answer:"We provide 24/7 doubt resolution through our TAI Bot, dedicated mentors, peer learning communities, and comprehensive career guidance throughout your journey."}]},courses:{category:"Courses",items:[{id:"available-courses",question:"What courses do you offer?",answer:"We offer Java Full Stack Development, and specialized courses in web development technologies. Each course is designed to make you industry-ready."},{id:"course-duration",question:"How long are the courses?",answer:"Course duration varies: Java Full Stack (4-6 months), The timeline depends on your pace and the depth of specialization you choose."},{id:"course-content",question:"What does the course curriculum include?",answer:"Our curriculum covers theoretical concepts, practical coding, real-world projects, industry tools, soft skills training, and interview preparation - everything needed for job readiness."},{id:"projects",question:"Will I work on real projects?",answer:"Yes! You'll build multiple real-world projects including e-commerce platforms, web applications that you can showcase to employers."},{id:"certificates",question:"Do you provide certificates?",answer:"Yes, we provide industry-recognized certificates upon course completion. These certificates are valued by our 3000+ hiring partners and enhance your job prospects."}]},placement:{category:"Placement",items:[{id:"placement-guarantee",question:"Is the placement guarantee real?",answer:"Yes, absolutely! We provide guaranteed job placement for students who complete the course and meet our assessment criteria. Our track record speaks for itself with 75,000+ successful uposkilled students."},{id:"salary-expectations",question:"What salary can I expect?",answer:"Our students typically receive offers ranging from ₹4-16 LPA depending on their skills, course completion, and performance. Many students see 200-300% salary increases."},{id:"hiring-partners",question:"Which companies hire TAP Academy graduates?",answer:"We have 3000+ hiring partners including TCS, Infosys, Solera, Detect,KPMG< Accenture, Amazon, Zeta, and many startups. Our placement team works continuously to expand this network."},{id:"placement-process",question:"How does the placement process work?",answer:"Our placement process includes resume building, mock interviews, technical assessments, soft skills training, and direct referrals to our hiring partners until you get placed."},{id:"placement-timeline",question:"How long does it take to get placed?",answer:"Most students get placed within 2-4 months of course completion. Our dedicated placement team provides unlimited interview opportunities until you succeed."}]}},Uz=ay,HE=f.forwardRef(({className:e,...t},n)=>a.jsx(Mi,{ref:n,className:F("inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center rounded-md p-1 text-muted-foreground",e),...t}));HE.displayName=Mi.displayName;const pu=f.forwardRef(({className:e,...t},n)=>a.jsx(Bi,{ref:n,className:F("inline-flex h-10 items-center justify-center whitespace-nowrap rounded-lg px-3 py-1.5 text-sm font-medium ring-offset-background transition-all focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring focus-visible:ring-offset-2 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 data-[state=active]:border data-[state=active]:text-foreground",e),...t}));pu.displayName=Bi.dis