                <br/>
                <p>Our program covers Full Stack Web Development in Java and Data Structures and Algorithms (DSA), offering hands-on learning with:</p>
                <br/>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                  <li>Core Java fundamentals and advanced concepts</li>
                  <li>Front-end technologies (HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React)</li>
                  <li>Advanced data structures and algorithms</li>
                  <li>Spring Boot and microservices architecture</li>
                  <li>Database design and optimization</li>
                  <li>Real-world project development</li>
                </ul>`},{id:2,imgUrl:rs.hire5,title:"Doubt Class",content:`<p><strong>Get your doubts cleared by experts in real-time</strong></p>
                <br/>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                  <li><strong>Live interactive sessions</strong> with mentors for immediate doubt clearance</li>
                  <li><strong>24/7 support</strong> and quick query resolution through dedicated Slack groups</li>
                  <li><strong>Access recorded class sessions</strong> anytime for review and clarity</li>
                  <li><strong>AI-driven assignments</strong> through the TAI Portal</li>
                  <li><strong>Extensive Drives Portal</strong> with unlimited placement opportunities</li>
                  <li><strong>Lifetime access</strong> to class recordings and AR training videos</li>
                </ul>`},{id:3,imgUrl:rs.hire8,title:"Practical",content:`<p><strong>Enhance your skills with hands-on experience through our digital platforms:</strong></p>
                <br/>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                  <li><strong>Apply your knowledge</strong> to live projects and assignments via the TAI portal</li>
                  <li><strong>Participate in virtual practice sessions</strong> that simulate real-world challenges</li>
                  <li><strong>Get instruction and feedback</strong> from industry professionals to refine your skills</li>
                  <li><strong>Work on industry-relevant projects</strong> that employers value</li>
                  <li><strong>Build a portfolio</strong> of real applications and solutions</li>
                </ul>`},{id:4,imgUrl:rs.hire9,title:"Placement Cell",content:`<p><strong>Receive dedicated support for your career advancement with our comprehensive placement services:</strong></p>
                <br/>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                  <li><strong>Resume Building Workshops</strong> - Create industry-standard resumes that get noticed</li>
                  <li><strong>Mock Interviews</strong> - Practice with real interview scenarios and feedback</li>
                  <li><strong>Job placement assistance</strong> - Direct connections with 500+ hiring partners</li>
                  <li><strong>Career Counseling and Guidance</strong> - Personalized career roadmap planning</li>
                  <li><strong>Salary negotiation support</strong> - Get the best possible offers</li>
                </ul>`},{id:5,imgUrl:rs.hire6,title:"Resources",content:`<p><strong>Access a wealth of materials and support to enhance your learning experience:</strong></p>
                <br/>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2">
                  <li><strong>Dedicated Notes for Each Technology</strong> - Comprehensive study materials</li>
                  <li><strong>1:1 Mentorship</strong> - Personal guidance from industry experts</li>
                  <li><strong>Access to TAP Academy Exclusive Platforms</strong> - Proprietary learning tools</li>
                  <li><strong>Practice Tests and Quizzes</strong> - Regular assessments to track progress</li>
                  <li><strong>Continuous Updates on latest technologies</strong> - Stay current with industry trends</li>
                  <li><strong>Community support</strong> - Network with peers and alumni</li>
                </ul>`}],s=[{src:ue.java,alt:"Java",category:"Backend"},{src:ue.spring,alt:"Spring Boot",category:"Backend"},{src:ue.hibernate,alt:"Hibernate",category:"Backend"},{src:ue.mysql,alt:"MySQL",category:"Database"},{src:ue.html,alt:"HTML5",category:"Frontend"},{src:ue.css,alt:"CSS3",category:"Frontend"},{src:ue.javascript,alt:"JavaScript",category:"Frontend"},{src:ue.vscode,alt:"VS Code",category:"Tools"},{src:rs.eclipse,alt:"Eclipse",category:"Tools"},{src:ue.claude,alt:"Claude",category:"Tools"},{src:ue.bolt,alt:"Bolt",category:"Tools"},{src:ue.cursor,alt:"Cursor",category:"Tools"},{src:ue.v0,alt:"V0",category:"Tools"},{src:ue.lovable,alt:"Lovable",category:"Tools"},{src:ue.githubCopilot,alt:"Github Copilot",category:"Tools"},{src:ue.windsurf,alt:"Windsurf",category:"Tools"},{src:ue.chatgpt,alt:"ChatGPT",category:"Tools"}];return a.jsxs("div",{className:"flex flex-col",children:[a.jsx(hJ,{}),a.jsx(CY,{openDemoModal:e}),a.jsx(NY,{logos:s}),a.jsx(OY,{}),a.jsx(PY,{data:n}),a.jsx(RY,{openDemoModal:e,jobRoleOptions:t}),a.jsx("section",{className:"section-layout--bordered",children:a.jsx("div",{className:"py-16 content-container container-padding",children:a.jsx(ne,{direction:"up",delay:0,children:a.jsx(bq,{sections:zz,title:"Frequently Asked Questions",subtitle:"Everything you need to know about hiring from TAP Academy",badgeText:"FAQs",defaultTab:"hiring"})})})}),a.jsx("section",{className:"section-layout--bordered",children:a.jsx("div",{className:"py-16 content-container container-padding",children:a.jsx(ne,{direction:"up",delay:0,children:a.jsx(iJ,{})})})}),a.jsx("section",{className:"section-layout--bordered",children:a.jsx("div",{className:"py-16 content-container container-padding",children:a.jsx(ne,{direction:"up",delay:0,children:a.jsx(pq,{})})})})]})}function BY(){return a.jsx("div",{className:"min-h-screen bg-[#1c2026] text-[#f5f5f5] pt-16 xs:pt-20 sm:pt-24 md:pt-32 pb-8 xs:pb-12 sm:pb-16",children:a.jsxs("div",{className:"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-3 xs